#. Tag: title
#: guides.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Detailed Guides"
msgstr "Podrobni vodiči"

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "This chapter describes how to perform some common tasks in &stage;."
msgstr ""
"V tem poglavju je opisano, kako izvajati nekatera običajna opravila v "
"&stage;."

#. Tag: title
#: guides.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a &HTML; Slideshow"
msgstr "Ustvari &HTML; Predstavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Turn an existing presentation into standard &HTML; pages with accompanying "
"navigation aids."
msgstr ""
"Spremenite obstoječo predstavitev v standardni &HTML; strani s "
"spremljajočimi navigacijskimi pripomočki."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, either make a new presentation, or open an existing one. Then, click "
"on <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Export as HTML...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Najprej naredite novo predstavitev ali odprite obstoječo. Nato kliknite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izvozi kot HTML...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "You will then get a dialog box asking for a few details:"
msgstr ""
"Nato boste dobili pogovorno okno, ki vas bo vprašalo za nekaj podrobnosti:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: guides.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Fill in the details for your &HTML; slideshow</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Izpolnite podrobnosti za svojo &HTML; predstavitev</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: guides.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Fill in the details for your &HTML; slideshow</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izpolnite podrobnosti za svojo &HTML; predstavitev</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fill in <guilabel>Title</guilabel> and <guilabel>Author</guilabel> fields. "
"Select the slides which should be exported. If you want to change a name "
"used on the &HTML; page for each slide double click on the name and edit it "
"inline."
msgstr ""
"Izpolnite polji <guilabel>Naslov</guilabel> in <guilabel>Avtor</guilabel>. "
"Izberite prosojnice, ki jih želite izvoziti. Če želite spremeniti ime, "
"uporabljeno v datoteki &HTML; stran za vsako prosojnico dvakrat kliknite na "
"ime in jo uredite v vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Output preview</guilabel> area the downsized slides are "
"displayed and you can check the correct slide order and browse the "
"presentation with the <guiicon>&lt;</guiicon> and <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> "
"buttons."
msgstr ""
"V območju <guilabel>Predogled izhoda</guilabel> so prikazani pomanjšane "
"prosojnice in lahko preverite pravilni vrstni red prosojnic ter brskate po "
"predstavitvi z <guiicon>&lt;</guiicon> in <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> gumbi."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now you can select a stylesheet with the configuration of the &HTML; options."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj lahko izberete slogovno datoteko s konfiguracijo datoteke možnosti "
"&HTML;."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To actually produce your &HTML; presentation, press the <guibutton>Export</"
"guibutton> button and select a folder."
msgstr ""
"Za dejansko izdelavo vaše &HTML; predstavitev pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Izvozi</guibutton> in izberite mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"What we now have are the newly-produced <filename>html/</filename> and "
"<filename>pics/</filename> folders, created where we earlier set the path:"
msgstr ""
"Kar imamo zdaj, sta na novo proizvedeni mapi <filename>html/</filename> in "
"<filename>pics/</filename>, ustvarjeni tam, kjer smo prej nastavili pot:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: guides.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The newly created &HTML; slideshow folders</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Novo ustvarjene &HTML; mape predstavitev</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: guides.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The newly created &HTML; slideshow folders</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Novo ustvarjene &HTML; mape predstavitve</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also an <filename>index.html</filename> file to launch your web "
"slideshow."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja tudi datoteka <filename>index.html</filename> za zagon vaše spletne "
"predstavitve."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can see how it works by using your file manager or web browser to open "
"the <filename>index.html</filename> file. Click where prompted, and the "
"first slide of your presentation is displayed. It will now behave as a "
"&stage; slideshow."
msgstr ""
"Kako deluje, si lahko ogledate tako, da z upraviteljem datotek ali spletnim "
"brskalnikom odprete datoteko <filename>index.html</filename>. Kliknite, kjer "
"ste pozvani, in prikazala se bo prva prosojnica vaše predstavitve. Zdaj se "
"bo obnašala kot &stage; predstavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each click on the arrow icons take you to the next or previous slide. To get "
"back to the start of the slideshow click on the slide icon."
msgstr ""
"Vsak klik na puščične ikone vas popelje na naslednjo ali prejšnjo "
"prosojnico. Za vrnitev na začetek predstavitve kliknite ikono prosojnice."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To share your presentation with the world, transfer the newly-produced files "
"to a network-accessible location (&ie; webspace), remembering to keep the "
"folder structure intact."
msgstr ""
"Če želite deliti svojo predstavitev s svetom, prenesite novo izdelane "
"datoteke na omrežno dostopno lokacijo (&ie; spletno mesto), pri čemer ne "
"pozabite ohraniti strukture map nedotaknjene."

#. Tag: title
#: guides.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating &stage; Templates"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje &stage; Predloge"

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "It is very easy to create a new template for &stage;."
msgstr "Ustvariti novo predlogo za &stage; je zelo enostavno."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have made a presentation in a style that you would like to use again, "
"you can save it as a template."
msgstr ""
"Če ste naredili predstavitev v slogu, ki bi ga radi ponovno uporabili, jo "
"lahko shranite kot predlogo."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tutorial will show how we can make a new template and save it."
msgstr ""
"Ta vadnica bo pokazala, kako lahko naredimo novo predlogo in jo shranimo."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open &stage; and create a new document."
msgstr "Odpri &stage; in ustvari nov dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a little sparkle to the blank slide, we can change the slide "
"background - do this by selecting the <guilabel>Document background</"
"guilabel> tool in the Tools docker."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati malo iskrice prazni prosojnici, lahko spremenite ozadje "
"prosojnice - to storite tako, da izberete orodje <guilabel>Ozadje dokumenta</"
"guilabel> v oknu Orodja."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We want the background to look attractive, so you may choose to use an image "
"as a background by clicking the <guibutton>Set image</guibutton> button: "
"feel free to experiment, but keep it beautiful!"
msgstr ""
"Želimo, da je ozadje videti privlačno, zato se lahko odločite za uporabo "
"slike kot ozadja s klikom na gumb <guibutton>Nastavi sliko</guibutton>: "
"lahko eksperimentirate, vendar naj bo lepo!"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: guides.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Choosing a slide background</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izbira ozadja prosojnice</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: guides.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Choosing a slide background</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izbira ozadja prosojnice</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The page should now have the background you desire. Create a text box, and "
"type a heading for your slide:"
msgstr ""
"Stran mora zdaj imeti želeno ozadje. Ustvarite besedilno polje in vnesite "
"naslov za prosojnico:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: guides.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Adding a Heading to the new template</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dodajanje naslova v novo predlogo</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: guides.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Adding a Heading to the new template</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dodajanje naslova novi predlogi</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are happy with your template, go to <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save As</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and select "
"<guilabel>Opendocument Presentation Template</guilabel> filetype in the file "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste zadovoljni s svojo predlogo, pojdite na "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani kot</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in v datoteki izberite vrsto datoteke "
"<guilabel>Opendocument Presentation Template</guilabel> dialog."

